io.github.struppigel.parser.sections

Class SectionHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.struppigel.parser.Header<SectionHeaderKey>
      • io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.SectionHeader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PEModule

    public class SectionHeader
extends Header<SectionHeaderKey>
    Represents an entry of the SectionTable.

    The instance is usually created by the SectionTable.
